March 2 (Reuters) - Vietnam Manufacturing And Export Processing Holdings Ltd:
* EXPECTS ‍TO INCREASE SIGNIFICANTLY​ FOR FY * ‍LOSSES OF GROUP FOR YEAR ENDED 31 DECEMBER 2017 ARE EXPECTED TO INCREASE​
* VIETNAM MANUFACTURING AND EXPORT PROCESSING HOLDINGS - EXPECTED RESULT DUE TO DECREASE IN SALES VOLUME & GROSS PROFIT MARGIN CAUSED BY COMPETITION​ Source text for Eikon: Further company coverage:
